Reverse a number:

Answer:

	// Reverse number
		int n=12345;
		int reverse = 0;
		
		while (n>0) {
		    //last digit
		    int lastDigit = n%10;
		    // add the last digit with the already reverse value. first time reverse value will be 0 multiply by 10 is 0
		    reverse = reverse * 10 + lastDigit;
		    //remaining number
		    n=n/10;
		}
		System.out.println(reverse);
